37 template <int N>
38 class Stoich
39 {
40 public:
41  Stoich(){
42  m_rxn = 0;
43  for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) m_sps[i] = 0;
44  }
45 
46  inline void multReaction(
47  const Eigen::VectorXd& p_s, Eigen::VectorXd& p_r) const
48  {
49  for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) p_r(m_rxn) *= p_s(m_sps[i]);
50  }
51 
52  inline void incrReaction(
53  const Eigen::VectorXd& p_s, Eigen::VectorXd& p_r) const
54  {
55  for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) p_r(m_rxn) += p_s(m_sps[i]);
56  }
57 
58  inline void decrReaction(
59  const Eigen::VectorXd& p_s, Eigen::VectorXd& p_r) const
60  {
61  for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) p_r(m_rxn) -= p_s(m_sps[i]);
62  }
63 
64  inline void incrSpecies(
65  const Eigen::VectorXd& p_r, Eigen::VectorXd& p_s) const
66  {
67  for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) p_s(m_sps[i]) += p_r(m_rxn);
68  }
69 
70  inline void decrSpecies(
71  const Eigen::VectorXd& p_r, Eigen::VectorXd& p_s) const
72  {
73  for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) p_s(m_sps[i]) -= p_r(m_rxn);
74  }
75 
76 protected:
77  size_t m_rxn;
78  size_t m_sps[N];
79 
80 }; //class Stoich<N>

84 class Stoich1 : public Stoich<1>
85 {
86 public:
87  Stoich1(size_t rxn, size_t sp1) {
88  m_rxn = rxn; m_sps[0] = sp1;
89  }
90 };

93 
94 class Stoich2 : public Stoich<2>
95 {
96 public:
97  Stoich2(size_t rxn, size_t sp1, size_t sp2)
98  {
99  m_rxn = rxn;
100  if (sp1 <= sp2) {
101  m_sps[0] = sp1; m_sps[1] = sp2;
102  } else {
103  m_sps[0] = sp2; m_sps[1] = sp1;
104  }
105  }
106 };
107 
108 //==============================================================================
109 
110 class Stoich3 : public Stoich<3>
111 {
112 public:
113  Stoich3(size_t rxn, size_t sp1, size_t sp2, size_t sp3)
114  {
115  m_rxn = rxn;
116  if (sp1 <= sp2) {
117  m_sps[0] = sp1; m_sps[1] = sp2;
118  } else {
119  m_sps[0] = sp2; m_sps[1] = sp1;
120  }
121 
122  if (m_sps[1] <= sp3) m_sps[2] = sp3;
123  else {
124  if (sp3 <= m_sps[0]) {
125  m_sps[2] = m_sps[1]; m_sps[1] = m_sps[0]; m_sps[0] = sp3;
126  } else {
127  m_sps[2] = m_sps[1]; m_sps[1] = sp3;
128  }
129  }
130  }
131 };
